items.title: How to turn off autoplay on your social media feeds
items.description: Here's how you can turn off autoplaying videos and GIFs on Facebook, Instagram, X, Twitter, and Threads.

items.title: Charlie Kirk Is Dead After Utah Valley University Shooting
items.description: Turning Point USA cofounder Charlie Kirk was shot at an event at Utah Valley University on Wednesday. He later died from his injuries.

items.title: OpenAI and Oracle reportedly ink historic cloud computing deal
